data.description: This five-bedroom, four-bath home epitomizes luxury and comfort. The kitchen is functional yet stylish, with new granite countertops, appliances, and custom hickory cabinets. The thoughtfully updated interior includes new hickory doors, welded handrails, and lighting with upgraded electrical switches and receptacles. Other features include a slate entryway, new flooring and trim, a wood stove, fresh paint, and an updated master bath. The exterior is a testament to curb appeal with cedar decks and meticulous landscaping, equipped with new irrigation, garage doors, roof, paint, security, and lighting. A standout feature is 1200 square feet of living space above the new garage with in-floor heating and 400-amp service. All appliances are included. Revel in the convenience of central air, providing climate control in both residences. This offering includes a $20,000 credit for siding, allowing you to complete this extraordinary residence in an established neighborhood. As a bonus, the property includes OLED televisions, a comfortable couch, a dining table, beds, and rugs.
